{"tid":1662980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發現新戰線!!!","createTime":"2019-10-19T06:22:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T06:37:37.000Z","uid":321572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b339fc3af6f9c68b1436acf026797cc234502c9","tid":1662980,"uid":321572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"九把刀問:<br />\n//因為小說取材關係，想問大家&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n現在的社會，從事什麼職業最丟臉最可恥？<br />\n我之前以為是賣假油，但好像不再是了......// <br />\n結果好多網民答<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察</strong></span>!<br />\n見另一個thread 都有講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1662868/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1662868/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n除左近排打嘅經濟戰線, 其實<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文化戰線</span></strong></span>仲有待開發<br />\n除左音樂/歌嘅攻勢, 我地仲可以向其實文化領域下手<br />\n好似<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">小說</span></span>, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">電影</span></span>, 影片等等<br />\n主題以反修例示威, 塑造前線為英雄, 或者以近日流傳嘅太子車站逃亡/香園圍, 作為懸疑推理作品, 一定大賣!! 同時亦可以為抗爭者做文宣, 確立形象<br />\n而近排見到嘅 e.g. 王喜有拍過&lt;警棍&gt;, 亦可以諷刺黑警, 希望有更多呢類影片<br />\n<br />\n個人認為建立我方軟實力, e.g. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">經濟圈/工會/文化滲入</span></span></strong>, 對長期抗爭極為重要<br />\n<br />\n最後想幫<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光時</span></span></strong>宣傳 <br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2F&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=9bbb5ad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/</a>"},{"pid":"3c7d8656124982368df0f0155b90f943916b42a1","tid":1662980,"uid":172638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 19<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------